<h2 id="chain-rule">Chain Rule</h2>

<p>μΈλΌμΈ μμ‹: \(\sum_{i=0}^n i^2 = \frac{n(n+1)(2n+1)}{6}\)</p>

\[\frac{\partial f\left(x,y\right)}{\partial x}\ =\ \frac{\partial \left(2x\ +\ 3xy\ +\ \combi{y}^3\right)}{\partial x}\\]
